the grave. Hebrew Sheol. App-35. Same word as"hell" ,Isaiah 14:9 andIsaiah 14:15 .

worm. This shows the meaning to be given to Hebrew"Sheol" in verses:Isaiah 14:9 ,Isaiah 14:15 ; as worms are material, not spirit. CompareIsaiah 66:24 .Mark 9:44, Mark 9:46, Mark 9:48 .

cover thee = are thy coverlet.
